#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2386
msgid "Transition"
msgstr "Transition（推移）"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2388
msgid ""
"A Transition decides - based on configurable conditions - which path in the "
"Process is taken, i. e. to which Activity a Process ticket can be moved."
msgstr ""
"推移は、設定可能な条件に基づいて決定します。プロセス中でパスが取得されている"
"ような条件です。。（例えば　プロセス・チケットが移動されうるアクティビティへ"
"のパスです）　　"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2392
msgid "Transition configuration"
msgstr "Transition configuration（推移構成）"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2394
