"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-ProcessProperties'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Process => {\n"
"            ProcessEntityID        => ['P1'],\n"
"            ActivityEntityID       => ['A1'],\n"
"            ActivityDialogEntityID => ['AD1'],\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3245
msgid "001-ACL-ProcessProperties"
msgstr "001-ACL-ProcessProperties"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3247
msgid ""
"Name of the ACL rule. For further information on ACL rules in general, "
"please consult <link linkend=\"acl\">the ACL manual</link>."
msgstr ""
"ACL規則の名前。ACL規則一般についてのさらに詳しい情報については、<link "
"linkend=\"acl\">ACLマニュアル</link>を調べてください:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3254
msgid ""
"This is the section that is used to check if an ACL must be applied. If it "
"has the specified values, the rule is applied. The following values can be "
"used:"
msgstr ""
"これはACLが適用されなければいけないかどうかをチェックするために使用されるセク"
"ションです。それが指定された値を持っている場合、規則が適用されます。次の値は"
"使用することができます:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3258
msgid "ProcessEntityID"
msgstr "ProcessEntityID"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3260
msgid ""
"The ID of a process that the process. Matches if the ticket is assigned to "
"this process."
msgstr ""
"プロセスのID、プロセス。チケットがこのプロセスに割り当てられる場合マッチしま"
"す。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3265
msgid "ActivityEntityID"
msgstr "ActivityEntityID"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3267
msgid ""
"The ID of the Activity that the process ticket currently is assigned to."
msgstr "プロセス・チケットが現在割り当てられるアクティビティのID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3271
msgid "ActivityDialogEntityID"
msgstr "ActivityDialogEntityID"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3273
msgid ""
"The ID of the Activity Dialog that is currently open for a process ticket."
msgstr "プロセス・チケットには現在開いているアクティビティ・ダイアログのID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3278
msgid "Possible/PossibleNot Activity Dialog"
msgstr "「可能」(Possible)/ 「不可能」(PossibleNot) アクティビティ・ダイアログ"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3280
msgid ""
"Here you can specify a list of Activity Dialog IDs. This list will limit the "
"possible Activity Dialogs that are offered to the user in the ticket zoom "
"mask."
msgstr ""
"ここでは、アクティビティ・ダイアログIDのリストを指定することができます。この"
"リストは、チケット・ズーム・マスク中のユーザに提示される可能なアクティビ"
"ティ・ダイアログを制限するでしょう。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3284
msgid ""
"'Possible' lists the Activity Dialogs that are allowed. The setting above "
"will only allow 'AD1' and 'AD3' of the list of configured Activity Dialogs."
msgstr ""
"「Possible（可能）」は、許可されるアクティビティ・ダイアログをリストします。"
"上記のセッティングは、設定されたアクティビティ・ダイアログのリストの「AD1」お"
"よび「AD3」のみを許可するでしょう。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3288
msgid ""
"'PossibleNot' lists the Activity Dialogs that are not allowed. In the "
"example above, the setting will remove 'AD3' from the list of configured "
"Activity Dialogs."
msgstr ""
"「PossibleNot（不可能）」は、許可されないアクティビティ・ダイアログをリストし"
"ます。上記の例において、セッティングは設定されたアクティビティ・ダイアログの"
"リストから「AD3」を取り除くでしょう。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3293
msgid ""
"If both 'Possible' and 'PossibleNot' are specified, the list of configured "
"Activity Dialogs will first be filtered by 'Possible', leaving only 'AD1' "
"and 'AD3' in our example. Then 'PossibleNot' will be applied and filter out "
"'AD3', so that only 'AD1' remains and is shown as a possible Activity Dialog "
"that the user can use."
msgstr ""
"「可能」と「不可能」の両方が指定されれば、設定されたアクティビティ・ダイアロ"
"グのリストはまず「可能」でフィルタされます。サンプルではAD1とAD3のみそのまま"
"残してあります。つぎに「不可能」が適用されます。「AD3」はフィルタで除外され、"
"それゆえに「AD1」のみが残り、ユーザが使える可能なアクティビティ・ダイアログと"
"して表示されます。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3300
msgid ""
"If multiple ACL rules match, the intersection of all matching rules will be "
"calculated to determine the possible Activity Dialogs. Example:"
msgstr ""
"複数のACL規則がマッチすればしたら、すべてのマッチング規則の共通部分は可能なア"
"クティビティ・ダイアログを決定するために計算されます。例:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3306
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-Status'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Status => 'new',\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'002-ACL-Queue'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Queue => ['Raw']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'003-ACL-Priority'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Priority => ['3 normal']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3', 'AD4'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-Status'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Status => 'new',\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'002-ACL-Queue'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Queue => ['Raw']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'003-ACL-Priority'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Priority => ['3 normal']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3', 'AD4'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3304
msgid ""
"Configured Activity Dialogs: 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD5', 'AD6', "
"'AD7'.  <placeholder type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/>"
msgstr ""
"設定されたアクティビティ・ダイアログ:「AD1」、「AD2」、「AD3」、「AD4」、"
"「AD5」、「AD6」、「AD7」<placeholder type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3339
msgid ""
"If a process ticket has the state 'new', is in the 'Raw' queue and has a "
"priority '3 normal', then all three ACL rules will match."
msgstr ""
"プロセス・チケットが状態「new」を持ち、それが「未対応」キューにあり優先度「3 "
"普通」を持つならば、その後、すべてのACL規則がマッチします。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3343
msgid ""
"The first rule reduces the Activity Dialogs from 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', "
"'AD5', 'AD6', 'AD7' to 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7' and forbids 'AD4' "
"and 'AD5'."
msgstr ""
"第一のルールはアクティビティ・ダイアログを 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', "
"'AD5', 'AD6', 'AD7'から'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7' に減らし、'AD4' and "
"'AD5'を禁止します。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3348
msgid ""
"The second rule will now further reduce the remaining Activity Dialogs.  In "
"our example, 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD7' will remain."
msgstr ""
"第二のルールはさらに残っているアクティビティ・ダイアログを減らし、ここでの例"
"の'AD2','AD3', 'AD7'が残ります。。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3352
msgid ""
"Now the third rule will further reduce the list by 'PossibleNot'.  'AD3' is "
"removed from the list. 'AD4' is not removed, since it was not on the list in "
"the first place. At the end, 'AD2' and 'AD7' remain as possible Activity "
"Dialogs that the user can utilize."
msgstr ""
"3番目の規則は、さらに「不可能」によってリストを縮小するでしょう。「AD3」はリ"
"ストから取り除かれます。それがリストの第一位に載っていなかったので、「AD4」は"
"削除されません。最後に、「AD2」および「AD7」は、ユーザが利用することができる"
"可能なアクティビティ・ダイアログとして残ります。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3358
msgid ""
"It is also possible to limit the processes that can be displayed in the "
"\"New process ticket\" screen, the functionality is similar to limiting the "
"ActivityDialogs with one exception: The ACLs could only be based on Users."
msgstr ""
"「新規プロセス・チケット」画面で表示可能なプロセスを限定することは可能です。"
"その機能は、ACLは単にユーザに基づくことができるという唯一の例外をもって"
"ActivitiyDialogs（アクティビティ・ダイアログ）を限定することに似ています。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3362
msgid "See examples below:"
msgstr "以下のサンプルを御覧ください。"

