"$Number $Unit\", where $Unit can be 's' (seconds), 'm' (minutes), "
"'h' (hours) or 'd' (days).  Only one unit can be specified. Examples of "
"valid settings: \"+50s\" (pending in 50 seconds), \"+30m\" (30 minutes), "
