#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea.xml:1942
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Figure: The dynamic fields overview screen with some dynamic "
"fields.</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>図: いくつかの動的フィールドを備えた動的フィールド概要画面</"
